Cerro Tololo and\nCerro Pachon with accuracy +-0\".1 (+-3 m). One surprise is that an oft-cited\nposition for LSST is in error by 9.4 km and the quoted elevation is in error by\n500 m.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 Oct 2012 00:21:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 10 Oct 2012 19:43:27 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 3 Mar 2013 20:14:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-03-05"}
