nal difference from N body result is within 1%. A merit of our\nmethod is that the computational time is very short because only single and\ndouble integrals are involved in our solution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 Oct 2012 07:17:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 30 Nov 2012 20:27:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-11"}
