ermine similar formulas and\nrelations for genus 3 hyperelliptic curves and offer an algorithm for how this\ncan be done for higher genus curves. It is still to be determined whether our\nformulas for $g=3$ can be used in cryptographic applications as in $g=2.$\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 Oct 2012 09:37:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-10-08"}
