egenerate Bose gas with infinite scattering length. We also\ndiscuss the generalization to arbitrary mixtures of bosons and/or fermions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 Oct 2012 15:21:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 11 Jan 2017 09:55:49 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 30 May 2017 13:33:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-05-31"}
